column2: "Oh... it's you. I have no interest in you. Where's that masked bastard?"
"But I guess you don't know anything about him, now do you?"
"Someone is out to kill you and you have no idea why, or even who he is? You're pathetic."

"<%me>, if you hide anything,
he will kill you where you stand."
"That's not gonna happen here, Sina. Where would the fun be in that?"
"But, from the situation the other day, it is impossible to conclude that they have no relation."
"Hmm, Sina? Are you telling me what to do?"
"You do as you like for now. Once you're ready, I'll have my fun."
